@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nxuqim(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.48 - v0 + 0.13) + (v2 + 0.86 * tmp + 0.91)))
    tmp = 0.75
    v0 = 0.60
    v0 = (wp.abs(v0) - (0.51 - wp.abs(v1 + 0.97)))
    v0 = (0.37 - (wp.abs(v0 + 0.22) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.66)))
    data[tid] = v0
